resume.html:
Specialized for several years in Typescript development, I like to develop FrontEnd applications, with libraries or frameworks like React or Angular. I like to design applications, think about their UI / UX.I want to be eco-responsible. My favorite hobbies are crafts and sports.

I am looking above all for a job with meaning.
